<p>Hi, I was interested by your description of the Robbers Cave Experiment, so I decided to do some research: from what I can tell no boys were killed in the process, and it was actually decently successful in the end  :-/  this website, <a href="http://www.age-of-the-sage.org/psychology/social/sherif_robbers_cave_experiment.html">http://www.age-of-the-sage.org/psychology/social/sherif_robbers_cave_experiment.html</a>  ,seems to have a pretty good description of the event.  :)</p>

